## tool-tavily-search: tavily_search tool definition

### tavily_search(query: str, search_depth: str = "basic") â†’ str
Search the web using Tavily AI search API. Returns an AI-generated answer summary plus source URLs.

Parameters:
  search_depth: "basic" (faster) or "advanced" (deeper, more thorough)

Use tavily_search when higher-quality, AI-curated results are needed, or when ddgs_search
did not return satisfactory results. Requires TAVILY_API_KEY.

This tool always requires human gate approval before it executes.
